title: [Arellis's Lockpicks]
description: A colorful Icemule map hangs on one of the plain wooden walls, and a blue plaster ceiling rises overhead.  A polar bear rug sits in one corner of an unfinished wooden floor.  There is a dovetailed oak table on one side of the shop and a long varnished counter on the other.

Beneath an oak beam ceiling, a colorful Icemule map hangs on one of the pale ivory plaster walls.  A dovetailed oak table and a long varnished counter sit in opposite corners while a polar bear rug rests on a bleached oak floor.
